structure.unit: RELIGIOUS, CHARITABLE, AND EDUCATIONAL SOCIETIES -- NONSTOCK, NONPROFIT CORPORATIONS

law.history: Repealed 1968 Ky. Acts ch. 165, sec. 70. -- Amended 1962 Ky. Acts ch. 210, sec. 46. -- Amended 1946 Ky. Acts ch. 150, sec. 1. -- Recodified 1942 Ky. Acts ch. 208, sec. 1, effective October 1, 1942, from Ky. Stat. sec. 319.

metadata.catchline-at-repeal: Religious society may not hold more than fifty acres of land for more than one year; escheat procedure.
